WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 27]

01:55.060 --> 01:55.930
Ji.

02:16.040 --> 02:16.810
Ji.

02:18.520 --> 02:19.690
I can see now.

02:20.240 --> 02:21.090
I can see now.

02:26.240 --> 02:26.970
Ji.

02:30.190 --> 02:31.020
Ji.

02:35.000 --> 02:36.090
Ji.

02:45.000 --> 02:45.770
Ji Ling.

02:47.280 --> 02:47.970
Ji Ling.

03:00.680 --> 03:01.420
Changsheng.

03:02.190 --> 03:03.460
Have you seen Ji Ling?

03:33.460 --> 03:34.140
[Bring health...]

03:34.140 --> 03:37.780
[Gather the essence of the universe to shield all magical harm.]

03:42.750 --> 03:43.900
A dragon scale

03:45.960 --> 03:47.250
banishes all curses

03:49.280 --> 03:50.740
and misfortunes...

03:51.560 --> 03:52.810
shields the spirit,

03:53.120 --> 03:54.370
and restores life from death.

03:55.590 --> 03:56.300
However,

03:56.630 --> 03:57.760
it settles only upon

03:58.960 --> 04:00.140
the one it deems worthy.

04:18.710 --> 04:19.530
Wu.

04:21.000 --> 04:22.570
To kill Jiu Ying,

04:23.720 --> 04:25.250
you must die.

04:29.160 --> 04:29.930
But the dragon scale

04:30.560 --> 04:32.220
can bring you back to life.

04:34.870 --> 04:35.660
However,

04:37.040 --> 04:39.180
not everyone can bear its power.

04:40.750 --> 04:42.130
But you've been through

04:42.360 --> 04:44.180
countless rewinds with Lonescale's power,

04:45.040 --> 04:47.220
creating a tie with the dragon scale.

04:48.630 --> 04:51.490
Maybe that's what it means to be the fated one.

04:52.950 --> 04:55.060
Your heart was once occupied by Jiu Ying's

04:55.950 --> 04:56.980
spirit fragment.

04:59.430 --> 05:00.540
From now on,

05:01.750 --> 05:03.890
let my dragon scale

05:05.040 --> 05:06.300
reside in your heart

05:09.120 --> 05:10.300
and stay with you forever.

05:11.980 --> 05:14.020
♪Through a thousand shadows...♪

05:14.270 --> 05:15.330
Don't be sad.

05:17.360 --> 05:18.180
Don't cry.

05:21.070 --> 05:22.620
I'll always be with you.

05:22.620 --> 05:25.100
♪Don't be sad♪

05:25.100 --> 05:26.460
♪Through every yesterday...♪

05:26.480 --> 05:27.690
Whatever you want,

05:28.310 --> 05:29.740
I'll bring it to you.

05:31.360 --> 05:32.450
You'll offer your heart

05:33.310 --> 05:34.180
if I want it?

05:35.830 --> 05:36.420
Yes.

05:39.980 --> 05:42.540
♪Don't be sad...♪

05:43.070 --> 05:44.180
You like Ji Ling.

05:45.160 --> 05:46.330
I like him, too.

05:47.480 --> 05:48.810
I've always liked

05:51.070 --> 05:52.780
my past self.

05:55.040 --> 05:56.860
So even if there is no future,

05:58.630 --> 05:59.740
there's nothing to regret.

06:00.060 --> 06:01.700
♪Through a thousand broken lights...♪

06:02.040 --> 06:03.130
But you are different.

06:05.190 --> 06:06.740
You hate your past.

06:08.190 --> 06:10.740
You never enjoyed a moment of happiness.

06:12.870 --> 06:13.930
So,

06:14.680 --> 06:15.450
Wu,

06:17.430 --> 06:18.660
you deserve

06:19.920 --> 06:21.660
a bright future more than I do.

06:24.260 --> 06:28.980
♪She holds a flower, counts the seasons slow♪

06:29.460 --> 06:31.980
♪Waiting for stone to bloom♪

06:32.340 --> 06:36.300
♪The flower in the mirror fades as I sketch it♪

06:36.780 --> 06:40.860
♪I remember the old days as I forget them♪

06:41.140 --> 06:44.100
♪Why's the line we cry to say♪

06:44.980 --> 06:49.380
♪Always "don't you cry"?♪

06:49.860 --> 06:53.700
♪Like sand slipping through fingers tight♪

06:54.140 --> 06:58.020
♪Your sunrise fades into my gray♪

06:58.500 --> 07:01.900
♪You left behind your final words♪

07:02.300 --> 07:07.020
♪And every word became a scar♪

07:07.300 --> 07:11.180
♪The flower in the mirror fades as I sketch it♪

07:11.740 --> 07:15.780
♪I remember the old days as I forget them♪

07:16.020 --> 07:19.100
♪Why's the line we cry to say♪

07:19.900 --> 07:24.340
♪Always "don't you cry"?♪

07:24.780 --> 07:28.660
♪Like sand slipping through fingers tight♪

07:29.220 --> 07:33.100
♪Your name's the words I long to say♪

07:33.500 --> 07:37.140
♪I call for you, my only one...♪

07:40.800 --> 07:42.060
Ji.

07:46.940 --> 07:48.130
Ji.

08:43.440 --> 08:44.330
He's dead.

08:46.600 --> 08:47.380
Finally,

08:48.910 --> 08:49.850
he's free.

08:51.670 --> 08:52.780
I have to go now.

08:58.390 --> 08:59.610
Who are you?

09:02.550 --> 09:03.850
I told you.

09:07.120 --> 09:08.260
I am you.

09:10.360 --> 09:11.570
You are me.

09:12.960 --> 09:13.660
We

09:14.240 --> 09:16.060
are Yuan Wuhuo's obsessions.
[*Wuhuo as in "free of misfortune"]

09:19.000 --> 09:21.260
I've always wanted to be your older brother

09:22.320 --> 09:23.540
and protect you.

09:25.270 --> 09:26.780
But many times,

09:28.390 --> 09:29.260
I thought

09:30.870 --> 09:32.420
you were supposed to be

09:32.420 --> 09:34.400
a carefree little fox.

09:38.960 --> 09:42.020
I hoped you could be freed from the shackles

09:42.020 --> 09:43.300
of the Dragon Deity's throne.

09:44.600 --> 09:47.260
I got you trapped here.

09:54.910 --> 09:56.500
What gives me the right

09:59.270 --> 10:00.540
to be your brother?

10:03.960 --> 10:05.300
I haven't achieved

10:07.360 --> 10:08.330
anything

10:10.030 --> 10:11.020
I wanted

10:13.480 --> 10:16.180
to achieve in my life.

10:19.550 --> 10:20.900
Before Yuan Wuhuo died,

10:21.480 --> 10:23.450
he had only two obsessions.

10:23.890 --> 10:26.650
One was to protect his brother forever.

10:27.420 --> 10:28.380
The other

10:28.790 --> 10:30.090
was to free Ji Ling

10:30.090 --> 10:32.660
from the lies.

10:35.790 --> 10:38.020
The good and evil twin six-eyed butterfly demons

10:39.030 --> 10:41.570
devoured Yuan Wuhuo's physical form

10:42.390 --> 10:44.140
and absorbed his two obsessions.

10:45.670 --> 10:47.810
Two completely different beings

10:48.390 --> 10:50.780
of good and evil split apart.

10:53.440 --> 10:55.420
That is, you and me.

10:57.360 --> 10:58.260
Li Jie

11:00.120 --> 11:01.450
and Yuan Wuhuo.
[*Wuhuo as in "gaining nothing"]

11:04.870 --> 11:07.140
I tried everything to kill him

11:07.910 --> 11:10.500
and free him from his endless pain.

11:13.080 --> 11:15.780
You tried your best to protect the Dragon Deity.

11:20.910 --> 11:23.180
We are nothing but the obsessions

11:23.600 --> 11:24.960
of a dying man.

11:24.960 --> 11:25.660
No.

11:32.120 --> 11:32.990
No.

11:35.910 --> 11:37.380
I may have come to Ji Ling

11:38.390 --> 11:40.730
because of the obsession.

11:43.670 --> 11:44.780
But all these years,

11:45.000 --> 11:47.930
I've witnessed his glory, pain,

11:48.550 --> 11:49.420
mercy,

11:50.270 --> 11:51.330
and loneliness.

11:52.000 --> 11:54.060
All this has nothing to do with you

11:54.390 --> 11:55.690
or the obsession.

11:56.870 --> 11:58.420
I did my best

11:59.550 --> 12:01.060
to serve the Shilin Sect

12:02.150 --> 12:04.450
out of my own will.

12:06.790 --> 12:07.660
Very good.

12:10.720 --> 12:12.570
But the person you want to protect

12:12.600 --> 12:13.610
has died.

12:15.240 --> 12:16.210
Now,

12:17.200 --> 12:19.090
who are you going to live for?

12:21.670 --> 12:22.610
Figure out

12:24.600 --> 12:25.810
the answer yourself.

12:27.030 --> 12:29.500
My obsession has already been fulfilled.

12:30.630 --> 12:31.570
He's dead.

12:32.720 --> 12:33.810
He's free.

12:35.120 --> 12:36.330
Now I have to go.

12:39.320 --> 12:41.090
The person I want to protect

12:43.720 --> 12:46.210
is waiting for me across the river.

12:46.420 --> 12:49.940
♪Quick footsteps, racing heart♪

12:50.460 --> 12:53.220
♪Busy running through the snow♪

12:54.460 --> 12:59.860
♪The person in my dream glows by the river♪

13:02.420 --> 13:05.940
♪The night wind is cold, my tears hot♪

13:06.460 --> 13:09.180
♪The one I love is ahead♪

13:09.700 --> 13:11.220
♪My homeland♪

13:11.660 --> 13:12.940
♪My strange land♪

13:13.060 --> 13:16.540
♪Both lit by fireworks♪

13:19.100 --> 13:24.380
♪In every daily necessity, there is nothing but longing...♪

13:29.840 --> 13:30.380
Father.

13:30.750 --> 13:31.420
Mother.

13:33.020 --> 13:33.500
Father.

13:33.540 --> 13:34.380
- Mother. - Brother.

13:34.680 --> 13:35.610
You're back.

13:35.650 --> 13:36.450
I missed you.

13:38.080 --> 13:39.500
Xizai, you've grown so tall.

13:40.840 --> 13:41.210
Brother.

13:41.510 --> 13:42.300
Have some.

13:42.630 --> 13:43.450
It's still warm.

13:43.750 --> 13:44.500
Give Xizai one.

13:44.840 --> 13:45.260
Come on.

13:45.630 --> 13:47.210
- I've eaten. - What?

13:49.030 --> 13:50.450
Mother's dumplings.

13:50.720 --> 13:51.330
Try it.

13:52.790 --> 13:53.540
You've lost weight.

13:53.870 --> 13:54.330
Try it.

13:54.790 --> 13:55.420
Come on.

13:56.120 --> 13:56.850
Eat more.

13:57.440 --> 13:58.140
Gain some weight.

13:58.270 --> 13:58.970
Be like me.

13:59.440 --> 14:00.060
Look at me.

14:05.580 --> 14:09.660
♪Who still remembers♪

14:10.140 --> 14:13.180
♪The child I used to be?♪

14:13.620 --> 14:15.380
♪Under the sparks of fireworks♪

14:15.620 --> 14:17.300
♪I gently clasped my hands♪

14:17.620 --> 14:22.860
♪Wishing for a life free of harm♪

14:41.120 --> 14:42.420
So this is the Formless Moon.

14:43.150 --> 14:44.450
What celestial air.

14:45.360 --> 14:46.020
Breathe it in

14:46.150 --> 14:47.570
and I'll live 500 more years.

14:48.320 --> 14:48.970
But

14:49.480 --> 14:50.730
why does it feel so cold?

14:55.030 --> 14:56.300
Traitor to the Formless Moon.

14:56.910 --> 14:58.500
How dare you bring someone here?

14:59.510 --> 15:00.450
Why are you here?

15:01.080 --> 15:02.260
To destroy the Oracle Stone.

15:02.720 --> 15:04.020
Destroy the Oracle Stone?

15:05.030 --> 15:05.900
Wu Wangyan.

15:06.120 --> 15:07.180
Are you crazy?

15:07.720 --> 15:09.180
The Sacred Spring doesn't lie.

15:09.550 --> 15:10.780
Memories don't lie.

15:11.670 --> 15:12.500
I came back

15:12.720 --> 15:14.330
to tell you

15:14.670 --> 15:15.690
the entire truth.

16:03.000 --> 16:04.420
Jiu Ying's spirit fragment

16:05.000 --> 16:06.930
has been hiding in the Oracle Stone.

16:07.360 --> 16:08.930
Jiu Ying has integrated his spirit

16:09.240 --> 16:10.610
with the Oracle Stone.

16:12.360 --> 16:14.260
The stone's power is everlasting,

16:15.150 --> 16:16.380
which sustains

16:17.080 --> 16:18.300
Jiu Ying's spirit.

16:19.240 --> 16:20.930
To kill Jiu Ying,

16:21.870 --> 16:22.660
we must

16:23.720 --> 16:25.450
destroy the Oracle Stone.

16:25.450 --> 16:27.080
[The old dragon falls. The new dragon rises.]

16:27.080 --> 16:28.680
[Heaven and earth tremble. Chaos fills the world.]

16:28.680 --> 16:30.580
[An old soul returns against time. A new moon reshapes the world.]

16:31.630 --> 16:32.450
This is

16:33.790 --> 16:34.900
the new prophecy.

16:36.080 --> 16:38.540
The old dragon falls. The new dragon rises.

16:39.270 --> 16:41.690
Heaven and earth tremble. Chaos fills the world.

16:42.910 --> 16:44.180
An old soul returns against time.

16:44.870 --> 16:46.300
A new moon reshapes the world.

16:47.360 --> 16:48.540
But nobody knows

16:49.030 --> 16:50.420
what it means.

16:52.740 --> 16:53.480
[The old dragon falls. The new dragon rises.]

16:53.480 --> 16:54.180
[Heaven and earth tremble. Chaos fills the world.]

16:54.180 --> 16:55.180
[An old soul returns against time. A new moon reshapes the world.]

17:00.840 --> 17:01.420
What's wrong?

17:02.200 --> 17:03.570
We're finally destroying this stone.

17:04.320 --> 17:05.330
Isn't that a good thing?

17:06.150 --> 17:06.930
Why do you guys

17:07.390 --> 17:08.540
look unhappy?

17:10.680 --> 17:11.650
- It's nothing. - It's nothing.

17:16.070 --> 17:17.500
More and more like a married couple.

18:39.000 --> 18:40.020
Finally,

18:42.510 --> 18:44.220
Jiu Ying is taken down.

18:46.240 --> 18:47.170
Master Dragon Deity

18:48.830 --> 18:50.060
would be happy, right?

18:52.640 --> 18:53.570
For so many years,

18:54.960 --> 18:56.650
he's been absorbing the dark power

18:57.000 --> 18:58.810
from those possessed

18:59.590 --> 19:01.090
by Jiu Ying's spirit fragments

19:02.440 --> 19:03.170
to shoulder

19:04.000 --> 19:05.170
the pain for those people.

19:08.680 --> 19:11.130
I want to see my grandson again.

19:15.750 --> 19:16.810
Despicable Dragon Deity.

19:17.160 --> 19:18.780
So what if you wipe me out?

19:19.350 --> 19:20.300
I am Jiu Ying.

19:20.640 --> 19:22.570
I am immortal.

19:24.960 --> 19:25.980
Too bad he won't be

19:27.750 --> 19:28.980
able to see this.

20:40.830 --> 20:41.980
These fancy garments

20:42.350 --> 20:44.220
have always been the worst curse.

20:45.160 --> 20:47.090
People burdened with longing carry an empty tomb

20:47.590 --> 20:48.410
in their hearts.

20:49.200 --> 20:51.220
Inside the tomb, no bones, just the clothes.

20:53.070 --> 20:54.220
This is life...

20:56.110 --> 20:57.500
You silly fox.

20:58.880 --> 21:00.540
Didn't you spend a lifetime

21:02.000 --> 21:03.850
wearing someone else's garments?

21:06.270 --> 21:09.260
Some people are destined to be like two mountains,

21:09.960 --> 21:11.320
gazing across vast grasslands,

21:11.350 --> 21:12.300
across canyons,

21:13.110 --> 21:15.060
across a distance that can never be closed,

21:15.590 --> 21:16.850
watching over each other.

21:17.880 --> 21:18.570
What

21:19.510 --> 21:20.810
are they waiting for?

21:21.480 --> 21:22.850
They're waiting for the snow.

21:24.110 --> 21:25.540
All it takes is a snow

21:26.310 --> 21:28.090
for them to be both crowned in white,

21:29.240 --> 21:30.410
as if they had grown old together.

21:35.920 --> 21:37.570
We've grown old together.

21:40.500 --> 21:43.580
♪Even apart, we still feel it all♪

21:44.420 --> 21:51.980
♪Like thousands of blooms on that shore♪

21:53.980 --> 21:58.700
♪At last, the moment is here♪

21:59.660 --> 22:06.340
♪You smile at me, but it's bittersweet♪

22:07.460 --> 22:11.540
♪Hand in hand, we walk side by side♪

22:13.940 --> 22:23.900
♪You're the brightest moon I know♪

22:24.540 --> 22:31.900
♪Sweetest berry that ever grew♪

22:34.020 --> 22:43.900
♪I was a drifter on the road♪

22:44.500 --> 22:53.380
♪Till you gave me a story to hold♪

23:02.460 --> 23:03.170
Thank you, Master.

23:05.850 --> 23:07.720
Bless us, Master Dragon Deity.

23:08.070 --> 23:08.940
I didn't expect

23:10.200 --> 23:11.500
that the story started here

23:12.240 --> 23:13.460
and ended here too.

23:15.000 --> 23:16.330
I wanted to kill the dragon.

23:17.310 --> 23:18.300
But now,

23:21.270 --> 23:22.650
I've become the dragon.

23:24.960 --> 23:25.610
Master Dragon Deity.

23:25.680 --> 23:26.610
Thank you for blessing me.

23:27.000 --> 23:28.020
These are all for you.

23:31.880 --> 23:32.780
Now you're obligated.

23:33.310 --> 23:34.170
It seems

23:34.640 --> 23:36.260
that you have to protect the commoners

23:36.510 --> 23:37.810
for the rest of your life.

23:40.950 --> 23:42.340
Thank you, Master Dragon Deity.

23:43.110 --> 23:43.650
Do you think

23:43.750 --> 23:44.780
he is the Dragon Deity?

23:45.240 --> 23:45.810
Look.

23:46.160 --> 23:47.940
Even the demon hunter commander is standing behind him.

23:48.200 --> 23:49.330
He must be the Dragon Deity.

23:49.960 --> 23:51.220
He will bless everyone.

23:51.590 --> 23:52.410
Yeah.

23:56.500 --> 23:58.310
- Yeah. - Yeah.

23:58.310 --> 23:59.330
Thank you, Master Dragon Deity.

24:14.750 --> 24:16.740
Humans are better than demons in one way.

24:17.350 --> 24:18.370
When a human dies,

24:19.550 --> 24:20.570
people set a tombstone

24:22.000 --> 24:23.300
and honor their memory.

24:24.440 --> 24:25.460
But when a demon dies,

24:26.440 --> 24:27.980
they are gone without a trace.

24:29.310 --> 24:30.170
If...

24:32.400 --> 24:33.540
I mean,

24:35.310 --> 24:36.370
if I can have

24:38.720 --> 24:40.700
a tombstone after I die,

24:43.440 --> 24:44.890
I would wish for the name on my tombstone

24:46.920 --> 24:48.020
to change

24:48.640 --> 24:49.850
from "Ji Ling"
[*as in "spirit vessel"]

24:51.920 --> 24:53.130
to "Ji Ling".
[*as in "spirit memorial"]

24:54.510 --> 24:56.090
I want to be remembered.

24:56.960 --> 24:57.980
I want to be mourned.

24:59.510 --> 25:00.850
I don't want to be

25:01.550 --> 25:03.500
nothing more than a spirit vessel.

25:05.830 --> 25:06.610
Rest assured.

25:07.400 --> 25:08.540
I'll protect you.

25:09.790 --> 25:11.130
I won't let you die.

25:33.350 --> 25:34.780
Master Ji Ling sacrificed himself.

25:35.240 --> 25:36.890
We shall inherit his legacy

25:36.960 --> 25:38.090
and guard the world.

25:39.550 --> 25:40.260
Master Ji Ling.

25:41.070 --> 25:42.020
I'll always remember

25:42.440 --> 25:43.740
the day you helped Luo'an City

25:43.960 --> 25:45.700
dispel the Fox-Allure Spell.

25:46.270 --> 25:47.330
The sky looked amazing.

25:47.960 --> 25:48.890
Master Ji Ling.

25:49.640 --> 25:51.460
Are you free now?

25:52.030 --> 25:53.020
I'm happy for you.

25:53.510 --> 25:54.810
Master Ji Ling.

25:54.880 --> 25:56.980
To me, you will always be the Dragon Deity.

26:03.640 --> 26:04.330
Ji Ling.

26:09.510 --> 26:11.220
You will never be forgotten.

26:28.500 --> 26:30.060
♪One winter day♪

26:30.980 --> 26:35.940
♪By the lake, a boy in white opened his eyes...♪

26:37.480 --> 26:39.570
Every time I came to this room,

26:41.960 --> 26:44.260
I took a new puppet.

26:44.260 --> 26:51.700
♪The wind asked why he smiled in silence...♪

26:55.030 --> 26:56.890
We only had to put this heart stone

26:57.240 --> 26:58.330
in its chest

27:00.590 --> 27:03.460
to get a brand new Ji Ling.

27:06.180 --> 27:12.420
♪He gazed at the sky, watching fate spin by♪

27:12.500 --> 27:18.860
♪The wind asked why he smiled in silence♪

27:18.860 --> 27:24.820
♪He bowed low, gently offering wildflowers from his heart...♪

27:25.400 --> 27:26.460
Again

27:27.830 --> 27:28.740
and again.

27:31.620 --> 27:37.700
♪Lights across the shore, snow trapped his lonely heart♪

27:38.100 --> 27:44.300
♪The moon curved above, a firework lit the sky bright...♪

27:45.000 --> 27:47.110
I should already be used to your death

27:47.110 --> 27:48.060
by now.

27:51.060 --> 27:56.700
♪Clad in golden scales, I gaze from the valley high...♪

28:00.160 --> 28:01.370
But now,

28:04.270 --> 28:05.300
you're gone for real.

28:05.300 --> 28:06.860
♪Bitter and sweet♪

28:07.060 --> 28:10.220
♪The moon stays by my side...♪

28:12.590 --> 28:14.610
You said you wanted a tombstone.

28:16.480 --> 28:18.260
So I'll bury this heart stone

28:18.440 --> 28:19.700
with you

28:21.240 --> 28:22.940
and make you a tombstone

28:24.960 --> 28:26.610
engraved with Ji Ling's name.

28:31.240 --> 28:32.410
"Spirit Memorial."

28:36.500 --> 28:44.020
♪She looks at me and says, you're not alone tonight♪

28:44.110 --> 28:45.260
Dragon Deity's Power.

28:50.440 --> 28:51.370
Master Chi Wen.

28:53.750 --> 28:54.720
This is the last strand

28:54.720 --> 28:56.460
of Dragon Deity's Power I left behind.

28:58.030 --> 28:59.410
This heart stone

28:59.960 --> 29:01.850
contains all the memories of Ji Ling.

29:03.000 --> 29:04.650
I'll take it to the Dragon Abyss,

29:05.350 --> 29:06.980
bathe it in the Sun and Moon

29:07.400 --> 29:08.980
to absorb the universe's essence.

29:09.830 --> 29:10.700
Maybe

29:11.510 --> 29:13.130
after thousands of years,

29:13.920 --> 29:15.260
this heart stone

29:15.880 --> 29:17.460
can form a shape through cultivation.

29:33.440 --> 29:34.300
Thousands

29:35.880 --> 29:36.850
of years?

29:41.510 --> 29:42.780
I can't wait that long.

30:00.920 --> 30:01.890
From now on,

30:02.200 --> 30:03.090
there are dragons

30:04.110 --> 30:05.020
once more.

30:07.640 --> 30:08.740
Jiu Ying has fallen.

30:09.680 --> 30:11.060
The mortal world regained peace.

30:11.790 --> 30:13.060
To the former Dragon Deity,

30:14.440 --> 30:15.260
my brother,

30:16.310 --> 30:17.170
Chi Wen.

30:26.830 --> 30:28.260
The former Dragon Deity

30:29.960 --> 30:31.060
was Ji Ling.

30:49.310 --> 30:50.220
Don't blame him.

30:53.070 --> 30:54.130
How could I blame him?

30:55.030 --> 30:56.020
Without Ji Ling,

30:57.480 --> 30:59.330
there would be no peace.

31:10.240 --> 31:10.980
Ji Ling.

31:12.000 --> 31:13.300
You are the real Dragon Deity

31:14.110 --> 31:15.300
to the people.

31:17.640 --> 31:18.570
Let's drink

31:19.480 --> 31:20.650
to the former Dragon Deity,

31:23.640 --> 31:24.300
Ji Ling.

31:31.920 --> 31:33.300
To Master Bai Ze.

31:36.310 --> 31:36.850
To

31:37.790 --> 31:38.850
Si Feng.

31:42.790 --> 31:43.980
To all those who died

31:45.110 --> 31:45.940
to save the world.

31:47.880 --> 31:48.610
And

31:49.550 --> 31:50.810
to the hardships we shared,

31:51.480 --> 31:53.220
and to Wu Shiguang for becoming a dragon.

31:53.590 --> 31:54.020
And

31:54.200 --> 31:54.650
to...

31:55.680 --> 31:56.130
To...

31:56.920 --> 31:58.130
To our precious friendship.

31:59.510 --> 32:01.170
You sure know how to cozy up to people,

32:01.350 --> 32:02.460
you little weasel.

32:03.000 --> 32:04.750
Hold on tight to the Shilin Sect token,

32:04.750 --> 32:06.020
or you'll be shattered.

32:20.750 --> 32:21.570
Wuyi.

32:33.310 --> 32:35.020
Wu Shiguang, Li Jie, and the others

32:36.750 --> 32:38.130
are drinking and celebrating

32:39.480 --> 32:40.850
under the golden-scale wood.

32:42.790 --> 32:43.700
Celebrating?

32:45.750 --> 32:47.130
What I mean is,

32:48.590 --> 32:50.220
it's not just about celebrating

32:50.240 --> 32:51.890
the death of Jiu Ying.

32:53.440 --> 32:54.130
On top of that,

32:55.830 --> 32:57.060
more importantly,

32:58.880 --> 33:00.540
they are commemorating Ji Ling.

33:01.790 --> 33:02.740
The golden-scale wood

33:03.310 --> 33:04.980
is full of ribbons for Ji Ling

33:05.110 --> 33:07.130
from demon hunters and common people.

33:08.960 --> 33:10.370
Don't you want to check it out?

33:12.790 --> 33:13.540
No.

33:20.550 --> 33:21.330
Wuyi.

33:23.000 --> 33:24.850
I thought I gave you my heart.

33:26.030 --> 33:27.330
But your true heart

33:27.750 --> 33:29.810
was Jiu Ying's spirit fragment.

33:31.720 --> 33:33.780
The last head of Jiu Ying was destroyed.

33:36.160 --> 33:38.330
And all the fragments faded away.

33:39.240 --> 33:40.940
You would have died.

33:45.200 --> 33:46.810
But Ji Ling kept you alive

33:48.480 --> 33:49.940
with his dragon scale.

33:50.750 --> 33:52.300
He surely wishes for you

33:52.590 --> 33:54.460
to live on, happy and well.

33:57.720 --> 33:59.940
I don't know what else I can do for you.

34:03.720 --> 34:04.330
But

34:06.310 --> 34:08.260
are you going to stay here forever?

34:10.000 --> 34:11.850
If Ji Ling could see you right now,

34:16.070 --> 34:17.130
he would never want you

34:17.190 --> 34:18.770
to be like this.

34:20.510 --> 34:22.340
Come back to the Formless Moon with me.

34:25.110 --> 34:26.060
I'll keep you company.

34:26.060 --> 34:33.060
♪Don't worry about me. Don't stay for me♪

34:33.220 --> 34:37.780
♪Great tree, O great tree♪

34:37.940 --> 34:41.700
♪Through snow and storm, you bend but breathe♪

34:41.980 --> 34:49.420
♪Let's set out toward the spring sunshine without fear♪

34:50.060 --> 34:53.740
♪Little grass, O little grass♪

34:54.020 --> 34:57.740
♪Rise on tiptoe, climb on bravely...♪

35:01.760 --> 35:02.380
Wangyan.

36:03.480 --> 36:04.540
Disturbing, huh?

36:05.630 --> 36:06.650
Painful, huh?

36:09.320 --> 36:10.170
Jiu Ying.

36:13.070 --> 36:14.650
You're still alive.

36:15.960 --> 36:17.210
As long as you're alive,

36:17.710 --> 36:18.770
I'll survive.

36:19.230 --> 36:20.940
What I put in your heart

36:21.000 --> 36:22.980
wasn't just my spirit fragment.

36:23.440 --> 36:25.090
There's also the Oracle Stone.

36:46.360 --> 36:48.500
I wasted half of my sacred power

36:48.880 --> 36:50.980
to cut out a small piece

36:51.110 --> 36:53.130
of the indestructible Oracle Stone.

37:25.000 --> 37:26.130
As long as the stone endures,

37:27.400 --> 37:28.650
I shall not die.

37:31.920 --> 37:32.650
Guess why

37:32.760 --> 37:34.610
I wrapped Wu Wangyan's heart

37:34.920 --> 37:36.190
around my spirit fragment

37:36.190 --> 37:37.730
I left in you.

37:38.510 --> 37:40.860
Because it's my biggest secret.

37:41.110 --> 37:42.670
This secret must

37:42.670 --> 37:44.130
remain undetectable to anyone.

37:44.800 --> 37:45.420
Now

37:45.800 --> 37:47.210
Ji Ling is dead.

37:47.840 --> 37:49.690
Wu Shiguang has become the new Dragon Deity.

37:50.280 --> 37:52.940
No one in this world will remember and honor Ji Ling

37:53.030 --> 37:54.130
except for you.

37:54.670 --> 37:55.730
And this longing

37:56.440 --> 37:58.820
will be your eternal shackles,

37:59.150 --> 38:01.340
torturing you forever.

38:02.920 --> 38:04.980
Why don't we set you free now?

38:05.480 --> 38:07.380
Hand over your physical form.

38:07.800 --> 38:10.420
Let your heart fly to the one you love

38:11.030 --> 38:12.420
and stay with him.

38:36.000 --> 38:37.020
Come with me.

39:00.710 --> 39:01.820
He's not gone.

39:03.440 --> 39:05.020
He's in my heart,

39:06.760 --> 39:08.210
keeping me company all along.

39:12.400 --> 39:14.460
You can wear human skin to look like him.

39:15.880 --> 39:17.690
But you'll never have

39:18.000 --> 39:19.860
his loving eyes.

39:22.670 --> 39:23.610
He loves me

39:24.230 --> 39:25.130
and the people.

39:26.800 --> 39:27.730
So,

39:30.480 --> 39:31.980
I won't let you ruin

39:34.320 --> 39:36.130
the world he has been guarding.

40:17.710 --> 40:18.980
We need to talk.

40:19.110 --> 40:20.060
Wait for me

40:20.510 --> 40:21.340
to come back.

40:22.760 --> 40:23.820
What's wrong with you?

40:24.280 --> 40:25.340
You're too busy to even

40:25.630 --> 40:26.770
talk to your brother?

40:27.150 --> 40:28.460
What are you talking about?

40:29.030 --> 40:30.730
You're the Dragon Deity now.

40:30.960 --> 40:32.130
Everyone listens to you.

40:33.670 --> 40:34.420
What about me?

40:34.840 --> 40:35.610
What do I do?

40:36.510 --> 40:37.170
What do you mean?

40:37.230 --> 40:38.020
You dog...

40:39.030 --> 40:41.060
When you're riding high,

40:41.320 --> 40:42.250
don't ditch your pack.

40:43.030 --> 40:44.610
You won't even let me stay in the Cosmic Pouch.

40:44.960 --> 40:45.730
I have nowhere

40:45.730 --> 40:46.500
to go here

40:46.800 --> 40:48.420
with terrifying formations everywhere.

40:49.150 --> 40:50.460
What am I doing here?

40:51.440 --> 40:52.650
We ran into danger

40:52.650 --> 40:53.610
several times out there.

40:53.880 --> 40:54.900
Have you forgotten?

40:55.630 --> 40:56.770
It's for your own good.

40:57.190 --> 40:58.250
You're not a weasel.

40:58.630 --> 40:59.610
You're an ungrateful brat.

40:59.670 --> 41:00.570
I'm not afraid of danger.

41:01.320 --> 41:01.880
I'm afraid of...

41:01.880 --> 41:02.500
Enough.

41:03.110 --> 41:04.460
You're obviously still drunk.

41:05.110 --> 41:05.940
We'll talk later.

41:17.550 --> 41:18.170
What's wrong?

41:19.630 --> 41:21.730
The last Dragon Deity's Power from Chi Wen

41:22.550 --> 41:23.900
took Ji Ling's heart stone

41:24.800 --> 41:26.020
to the Dragon Abyss.

41:26.840 --> 41:27.610
He said

41:28.230 --> 41:29.250
that the heart stone

41:29.630 --> 41:31.460
contains all the memories of Ji Ling.

41:33.480 --> 41:35.210
Maybe thousands of years later,

41:36.630 --> 41:38.250
it can cultivate into human form.

41:42.960 --> 41:43.900
That's great.

41:46.280 --> 41:47.770
Humans are mortal.

41:48.510 --> 41:49.940
I can't wait that long.

41:54.440 --> 41:55.500
But you can.

41:57.670 --> 41:59.090
If you see him,

42:00.590 --> 42:01.900
tell him

42:03.230 --> 42:04.060
that

42:06.030 --> 42:07.420
I've figured out who I am.

42:36.110 --> 42:36.820
Look.

42:37.440 --> 42:38.340
So sparkling.

42:39.440 --> 42:40.460
Doesn't it look like

42:41.510 --> 42:42.610
our former home?

42:47.110 --> 42:48.500
I remember that I liked

42:50.320 --> 42:51.860
waiting for you by the water

42:52.960 --> 42:53.900
in the illusion.

42:55.840 --> 42:56.730
This time,

42:58.440 --> 42:59.340
let me wait for you

43:00.440 --> 43:01.250
by the water.

43:03.760 --> 43:05.650
I'll be back in just a few days.

43:08.230 --> 43:09.570
That's long enough.

43:22.150 --> 43:23.170
This is...

43:25.400 --> 43:26.090
I

43:27.710 --> 43:29.090
added my dragon scale to it.

43:36.020 --> 43:40.860
♪A silent parting spreads like a sea of fog...♪

43:44.280 --> 43:45.860
Impressive craftsmanship.

43:51.710 --> 43:52.900
You once said

43:55.400 --> 43:56.340
that two people

43:59.230 --> 44:00.860
are like two rivers.

44:03.110 --> 44:04.610
They converge

44:07.000 --> 44:08.940
and change each other's course.

44:11.710 --> 44:13.500
But it seems our fates are headed

44:14.630 --> 44:15.500
in directions

44:16.190 --> 44:18.090
that will never let us grow old together

44:18.190 --> 44:19.290
like normal people.

44:20.550 --> 44:21.340
It's fine

44:22.880 --> 44:23.900
as long as

44:25.400 --> 44:27.250
I can stay with you forever.

44:31.340 --> 44:35.460
♪The ending in disarray, like youth drawing to a close...♪

44:36.030 --> 44:36.860
Wangyan.

44:41.510 --> 44:42.380
Marry me.

44:46.060 --> 44:47.380
♪Don't forget♪

44:48.180 --> 44:54.580
♪Watch the spring breeze stir the warm sun, flowers across the hills♪

44:54.980 --> 45:00.580
♪Summer days run long, and flowing rain carries me afar♪

45:01.340 --> 45:06.940
♪Autumn turns cool, and fallen leaves become the clothes of dreams♪

45:07.500 --> 45:12.460
♪A face worn old by wind, snow, and frost♪

45:13.580 --> 45:19.900
♪But my tears still burn hot♪

45:19.940 --> 45:26.020
♪There is a harbor with ripples dancing in my heart♪

45:26.220 --> 45:32.260
♪With hair gone white, we softly recount the story♪

45:32.460 --> 45:36.540
♪My time with you♪

45:37.860 --> 45:39.500
♪Lasts forever♪

45:53.400 --> 45:54.250
Sisters.

45:55.440 --> 45:56.250
We

45:56.920 --> 45:58.340
carried out many tasks

45:58.630 --> 45:59.900
assigned by Jiu Ying,

46:02.480 --> 46:03.940
causing a lot of tragedy

46:04.880 --> 46:05.940
beyond redemption.

46:10.440 --> 46:11.250
Wangyan.

46:11.960 --> 46:12.650
Let's go.

46:29.960 --> 46:31.130
I want to give it my all

46:32.110 --> 46:33.290
to redeem the errors

46:33.320 --> 46:34.460
I once made.

46:37.960 --> 46:39.500
But it's just my choice.

46:41.880 --> 46:43.900
You've dedicated everything to the Formless Moon.

46:44.670 --> 46:46.820
It's time to start your own lives

46:47.400 --> 46:49.060
and pursue true freedom.

46:50.000 --> 46:50.730
But

46:50.920 --> 46:51.610
I don't know

46:51.630 --> 46:52.820
what I want, either.

46:54.070 --> 46:55.210
I think I'm used to

46:55.230 --> 46:56.250
this lifestyle.

46:56.800 --> 46:58.900
I'm used to carrying out missions.

46:59.840 --> 47:01.500
Instead of searching aimlessly,

47:01.800 --> 47:02.500
why don't we

47:03.230 --> 47:04.460
make amends with you?

47:05.150 --> 47:05.860
That's right.

47:06.480 --> 47:08.650
We are sisters who share honor and disgrace.

47:09.190 --> 47:10.570
We should stand by each other.

47:13.760 --> 47:14.540
Wangyan.

47:24.000 --> 47:25.210
Formless Moon,

47:26.670 --> 47:28.290
submit to me.

48:12.020 --> 48:13.180
♪It's your light♪

48:13.380 --> 48:15.260
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

48:15.420 --> 48:18.540
♪That set the night alight♪

48:18.900 --> 48:25.420
♪And lead me through the fight♪

48:27.180 --> 48:29.060
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

48:29.500 --> 48:33.940
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

48:34.740 --> 48:36.420
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

48:36.580 --> 48:41.980
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

48:42.740 --> 48:48.140
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

48:50.460 --> 48:56.500
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

48:57.460 --> 48:59.620
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

48:59.900 --> 49:04.740
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

49:05.100 --> 49:07.420
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

49:07.620 --> 49:12.700
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

49:12.940 --> 49:14.940
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

49:15.220 --> 49:19.580
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

49:20.580 --> 49:27.540
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

49:44.100 --> 49:47.060
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

49:48.140 --> 49:51.540
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

49:52.340 --> 49:54.860
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

49:55.100 --> 49:58.180
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

49:58.580 --> 50:00.900
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

50:01.420 --> 50:05.820
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

50:06.060 --> 50:08.220
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

50:08.620 --> 50:13.580
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

50:13.820 --> 50:14.980
♪It's your light♪

50:15.180 --> 50:17.020
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

50:17.220 --> 50:20.340
♪That set the night alight♪

50:21.100 --> 50:30.540
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
